<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students who earn acceptable scores in the Advanced Placement Program of the College Entrance Examination Board will receive credit at Trinity providing they receive a grade of 3 or better and that all appropriate materials and scores are submitted to Trinity Records Office for credit evaluation.</i>
